								<name type="person" role="owner">Shelomoh ben Avraham</name>, <name type="person" role="owner">Shelomoh Supino</name>, <name type="person" role="owner">Shelomoh ben Yitsḥaḳ</name> and <name type="person" role="owner">Ya῾aḳov ben Mosheh</name>: inscribed, folio 134v.</p>
							<p>Folios 134v-135r contain doodles. </p>
						</additions>
